subtitleNullable: Information about all episodes of Naruto Shippuden
descriptionNullable:
### Context

I was watching One Piece and out of nowhere I started watching an episode that looked like a filler, but the platform I was watching didn't say whether or not it was, then after that, so every time I had to look on weird websites to see if the episode was filler , so I decided to create an application that would provide such information which can be consulted  [here](https://alissonrp.shinyapps.io/op_beta/) (beta version).   
Following the same idea, I also decided to create a database for Naruto, for those who watch anime, it is common knowledge that Naruto Shippuden has numerous fillers, so I decided to make this dataset available for those who want to analyze the episodes!


### Content

*  Num_episode: Number of respective episodes
* Title: Title of respective episodes
* Type: Type of episode (filler, cannon, etc)
* Year_launch: Episode release year
* Rate: Average Rate of respective episode
* Votes: Total of votes in the respective episode (11/29/2021)
* Saga: Season of the history
